## Anti-Patterns to Avoid
- ❌ N+1 queries
- ❌ God services (split responsibilities)
- ❌ Hardcoded configuration
- ❌ Missing error handling
- ❌ Not using transactions
- ❌ SQL injection (use parameterized queries)
- ❌ Storing sensitive data in logs
